about Talvinder way before.

50:21.518 --> 50:22.728
We were scared.

50:25.063 --> 50:26.106
She's scared.

50:27.149 --> 50:29.276
Not thinking straight,
and not knowing who to trust.

50:31.653 --> 50:36.158
[sighs]
But that doesn't make it right.

50:37.409 --> 50:39.119
And I didn't come here to make excuses.

50:41.413 --> 50:42.914
I just want to tell you the truth.

50:44.541 --> 50:46.126
From now on, no more lies.

50:47.753 --> 50:49.671
Don't make promises you can't keep.

50:53.633 --> 50:54.885
